    <item>
      <title>sShaman Prayers Have Been Heard By the Developers!</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=TNZ&amp;message.id=12912#M12912</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Hey again, guys.&amp;nbsp; I figured I'd post another status check for (most) of the shaman.&amp;nbsp; Turtle_Pet probably still disagrees, but, ironically,&amp;nbsp;he's changing classes to something guilds want.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Pretty much the only reason I'm bothering to post here is that we had a lot of people that I know weren't members of the Crucible come out and post in support, so I figured I'd give you guys a status update!&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;GoD has been out for a while now, as you well know.&amp;nbsp; People are getting to explore a few of the other zones.&amp;nbsp; Right now, most of the emphasis appears to be on the trials.&amp;nbsp; Sewer trials are 1-4, vexd trial is 5, tipt trial is 5.&amp;nbsp; I forget all the various names of 7-9, but they get harder.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;As the beta folks noted when the&amp;nbsp;confidentiality agreement&amp;nbsp;was over, mobs in GoD hit extremely hard and have low HP.&amp;nbsp; Trial mobs (the yard trash) in 5 and up hit for 1200s or so and double or triple.&amp;nbsp; The named in Trial 6 hits for 1800s and appears to be slowable by about 20%.&amp;nbsp; The nameds in trials 7+ aren't slowable at all, and hit 2200s or so.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Enter the shaman!&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;As you may recall, higher end shaman were already talking about a major lack of healing.&amp;nbsp; Elemental planes mobs and hard LDoNs, let alone LDoN raids make shaman deficiencies painfully clear.&amp;nbsp; Noting the severe LACK of healing upgrades in GoD, we tried to get a little attention from SoE.&amp;nbsp; Our prayers have been answered.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Clearly, even the developers have noticed that healing isn't sufficient for GoD.&amp;nbsp; As a patch that went in a couple of days ago on the test server, heals have been increased for healing classes across the board.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;The&amp;nbsp;numbers following the spells are&amp;nbsp;hp/mana.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Light of Order (pal) 935/440 1.0 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test:&amp;nbsp; 1000/430 1.0 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Holy Light (clr) 3050/660 3.75 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test:&amp;nbsp; 3275/650 3.75 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Sylvan Infusion (dru)&amp;nbsp;1925/550 3.5 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test:&amp;nbsp; 2100/550 3.5 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Sylvan Light (rng) 470/195 3.0 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test:&amp;nbsp; 525/195 3.0 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Tnarg's Mending (shm from PoP--no new heal in GoD)&amp;nbsp; 1300/450 3.75 cast time&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test: none&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Two classes got a new Heal Over Time (HoT) spell with GoD--shaman and clerics&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Holy Elixer (clr) 550/tic for 440 mana.&amp;nbsp; 4 tics. cast time 4.0&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test:&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Breath of Trushar (shm) 360/tic for 220 mana.&amp;nbsp; 4 tics.&amp;nbsp; cast time 6.0&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Changes on test: &lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
